Description: Flight into Egypt. Landscape with the holy family approaching a small bridge in the centre, ruins and a cascading river to the left, trees and a town in the background Etching
Curator's comments: This is fourth state with address of Crepy, for other states see S.4049-4050 and 1877,1013.776
